      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Secure your Ben2 api integration using OAuth 2.0 or API keys. For OAuth, obtain tokens via the "
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "/auth/token",
            "code": true
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " endpoint and include them in the "
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Authorization",
            "code": true
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " header. Rotate keys regularly and use scopes to restrict access. Implement TLS 1.3 for all communications and validate webhook signatures to prevent tampering."
          }
