            "text": "Implement robust error handling for Ben2 API responses. Map HTTP status codes to application logic, such as retrying on 429 (rate limit) or failing on 401 (unauthorized). Integrate with observability tools like Prometheus to track error rates and latency percentiles. Set up alerts for anomalies and log request IDs for traceability."
